## Recommendations

### VR002: Stop the non-preferred IM daemon [review before running]
Pick one framework and disable the other.

```
systemctl --user disable --now ibus
```

### VR003: Align IM env vars with the active framework [review before running]
Set GTK/QT/XMODIFIERS/SDL_IM_MODULE to one consistent value.

```
export GTK_IM_MODULE=fcitx
```
